Template: pse-server/skip-autoconf
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Skip autoconf?
 Skips automatic configuration.

Template: pse-server/public-uri
Type: string
Default: https://example.com/
Description: Public URI:
 The public URI under which the the PSE server is publicly accessible.

Template: pse-server/currency
Type: string
Default: USD
Description: Currency:
 The ISO-4217 code for the currency used by the server.

Template: pse-server/setup-db
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Setup the database?
 If set, the database will be automatically configured on the local PostgreSQL instance.

Template: pse-server/oidc-client
Type: string
Default: 
Description: OIDC client id:
 The OIDC client id of the PSE server.

Template: pse-server/oidc-discovery
Type: string
Default: 
Description: OIDC discovery URI:
 The OIDC discovery URI for the OpenID provider used by the PSE server.
